name: MYMAG
description: MYMAG is magazine created by tastemakers
overview:
MYMAG is an engaging personal media platform that enables a tastemaker to establish a greater connection with their fans. By creating their own magazine, the tastemaker can endorse content and brands which gives their fans greater insight into what makes them tick.

MYMAG is innovative, effective and beautiful in its simplicity. We take a well-loved format- the printed magazine- and combine it with the efficiency of social media to create a new connection for influential individuals and their supporters.
